{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_09_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚 3話 一緒に進めるように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　お待たせしました！\nステージは……琴乃ちゃんはどうなってますか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Sorry to keep you waiting!\nThe stage… How is Kotono doing!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今は二曲目だ。あと四十秒で曲が終わるから\nそのタイミングでステージに上がってくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's on her second song now. It'll be over in forty seconds‚\nso could you go on stage at that timing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 13.8333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！\n琴乃ちゃん……今行くよ。待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it!\nKotono-chan… I'm coming now. Wait for me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 20.433333842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、本当によく頑張ってるよ\n見えるだろう？　この舞台袖からでも、あの表情が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono is really doing a great job.\nEven from backstage‚ you can see that expression of hers‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.033333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 28.4666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……凄い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…… Amazing……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 32.5666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "よし、曲が終わったぞ\nみんな、一緒に盛り上げてきてくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ the song's over.\nEveryone‚ let's liven things up together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 37.9000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　行ってきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'm off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日、MV撮影の現場にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Next Day‚ At the Music Video Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6660308999965,
          "startTime": 42.4000003815
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0333353678
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0333353678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "渚、お疲れ様。昨日のフェスから立て続けで\nハードだと思うが、頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ good work. You've been going non-stop since yesterday's festival‚\nso it must be tough‚ but do your best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.0333357492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　頑張っちゃいますよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'll do my best~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0333357492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "凄いやる気だな。何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're really motivated. Did something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9999996184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……\nこの間まで目標についてず～っと悩んでましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe……\nI was worrying about my goals all the time until recently‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.1666650135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のフェスで、一人でステージに立つ琴乃ちゃんを\n見て……一気に考えがまとまりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At yesterday's festival‚ I saw Kotono standing on stage by herself‚\nand…… all of a sudden‚ my thoughts came together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9333296457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが言ってくれたように\nきっかけ一つでこんなに変わるもんなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like {user}-san said‚\na single trigger can change things this much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だからそんなにすっきりした顔をしてるのか\nでも、琴乃がきっかけってどういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's why you have such a refreshed expression.\nBut‚ what do you mean Kotono was the trigger?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.1999963123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人が駆け付けた時……一人であれだけ堂々と\n歌っていた琴乃ちゃんが、満面の笑みを浮かべたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we four rushed over there… Kotono-chan‚ who had been singing\nso confidently all by herself‚ was wearing the biggest smile on her face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0333271025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "あの後琴乃ちゃんに聞いたら、私達を見つけた瞬間に\n肩の力が抜けて、凄く安心したらしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Afterwards‚ when I asked Kotono-chan‚ she said that at the moment she found us‚\nthe weight on her shoulders lifted‚ and she felt incredibly relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.7666589099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで私、思ったんです。「ああ、私には琴乃ちゃんが\n必要で……琴乃ちゃんも私のことが必要なんだ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what made me think‚ \"Ah‚ I need Kotono-chan‚\nand Kotono-chan needs me.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2666578927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ステージでのほんの少しのやりとりだけで\n答えが見えることもあるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you can find the answer with\njust a little bit of interaction on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0330620302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとの関係は\n変わった部分も、もちろんあるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The relationship with Kotono\nhas changed in some ways‚ of course…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7333245593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんを支えたい、っていう根っこの部分は\nやっぱり変わってませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but my core feeling that I want to support Kotono-chan\nhasn't changed at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0666507719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけじゃなくて……今は、私自身も輝いて\n胸を張って琴乃ちゃんと並び立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ that’s not all… right now‚ I want to shine as well‚\nand stand proudly‚ shoulder to shoulder with Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8000039418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.0999706085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "そして、お互いを支え合って……「お互いを一番近くで\n照らし合える関係」になりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ while supporting each other… I want us to be in a relationship\nwhere we can illuminate each other at the side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2000039418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.0666548409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
