      "text": "はい。それが、月ストを支えることにもなるのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I think that will also lead to supporting Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0333215075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
