      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なんですかね\nえへへ……嬉しいです",
