      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "（だけど、私達は暗闇の中で道に迷って）\n（離れ離れになって、それぞれの道を進むことになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ we got lost in the darkness）\n（and got separated‚ and ended up walking our own paths.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.633341344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "（結果的にまた五人に戻れたけど、もしかしたらもう）\n（琴乃ちゃんとは二度と会えなくなってたかもしれない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the end‚ the five of us came together again‚）\n（but I thought we might never see you again.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.3666929879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs028.m4a",
      "text": "（だからね。私、決めたんだ）\n（今度は私が琴乃ちゃんの道を照らしてみせる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's why I've made up my mind.）\n（This time‚ I'll illuminate Kotono-chan's path.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.9333433785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs029.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃんが迷わず、勇気を持って一歩を踏み出せる）\n（ように。これからの道のりを一緒に進めるように）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So that Kotono-chan can take a step forward without hesitation and with）\n（courage. So that we can move forward together on the path ahead.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.5333677925,
      "sfxList": []
