      "text": "（渚……優しくて、だけどとても力強い表情をしてる）\n（また一つ、成長したみたいだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Nagisa… has a kind yet very strong expression on her face.）\n（It seems like she's grown up another step.）",
